name: Frog Frenzy
description:
Frog hoppin' fun! Froggy is trying to escape the city... but he can't swim and needs your help. Guide Froggy through treacherous traffic and across bodies of water to reach his goal. Grab power-ups along the way to make the journey easier. Be careful, because some items are dangerous and can impede Froggy's progress. Incredible all new 3D graphics, cool music and non-stop arcade action!

Features

* Over 20 amazing levels
* Cool power-ups
* High-score table
* Addicting game-play
* Super Cool soundtrack
* Classic retro arcade fun
